name: Laser Eyes
description: Laser Eyes Club is a community whose main vision is to fight scams, educate everyone about blockchain and create various utility products. To fight this rug/scams, Laser Eyes came up with an automated tool where you can enter the contract address to get an automated analysis of the same. It is currently in the BETA version currently. Laser Eyes Scan: It is the first product of Laser Eyes Club. Laser Eyes Scan is currently in Beta and it helps you to identify the rug/fraud projects. Laser Eyes Scan is an automated tool with thousands of visitors every month. A future update of Laser Eyes Scan will include features such as screening source code for scam functions, checking LP status, checking ownership status, checking dev wallet history, and many more.
